transcript:
Customer: Hello

Executive: Hello
Customer: Hello
Executive: Ha kaun?
Customer: Sir good evening.
Executive: Ha bolo.
Customer: Ye Sudhir Industries ko baat kar rahi hai na Sudesh Sudesh baat kar rahi hai. Ha aap karwari hai. Sir mera naam parash India Mart ke head office se baat kar raha hu main aapka business manager. Kaise hai aap?
Executive: Ha bolo.
Customer: Actually main call isliye kar raha tha aapko ek miss call aaya hua tha main check kar raha tha. Aapke account manager ke paas 14 tarikh ko aapne shayad call kiya tha evening mein 6:30 baje ke aas paas.
Executive: Ha.
Customer: To jante aapke sath issue face kar rahe the isliye contact kar sakte the ya matlab by mistake laga raha call ye.
Executive: Kya matlab kaunsa kya bol rahe the aapki aawaz nahi aa rahi thi. Main ye puch raha hu aapne na apne account manager ko call kiya tha 14 tarikh ko Friday ko evening mein 6:30 baje ke aas paas. Main nahi kiya. Ha shayad galti se lag gaya hoga call bhi wahi. Okay okay okay. Theek hai sir main yaha update kar de raha hu concern ko close kar de raha hu. Aapke paas jo feedback aayega wo please feedback share kar dijiyega. Theek hai theek hai. Aur koi issue to nahi hai sir koi services mein koi issue koi problem aap face kar rahe hai. Nahi nahi koi issue nahi hai. In case agar koi issue ya problem aaye to please mujhe yaha par update kijiye sir. Okay okay sure theek hai. Okay sir thank you aap feedback de dijiye.
Executive: Okay.
